To view what's written in a file - cat filename
To change the access permissions of files - chmod +rwx / chmod 777
To check which commands you have run till now - history
To remove a directory/ Folder - rmdir directory name
To create a fruits.txt file and to view the content - touch fruits.txt and cat fruits.txt
Add content in devops.txt (One in each line) - echo 'Apple, Mango, Banana, Cherry, Kiwi, Orange, Guava' >> devops.txt
To Show only top three fruits from the file - cat devops.txt | head -3 
To Show only bottom three fruits from the file - cat devops.txt | tail -3
To create another file Colors.txt and to view the content - touch colors.txt and cat colors.txt
Add content in Colors.txt (One in each line) - echo 'Red, Pink, White, Black, Blue, Orange, Purple, Grey' >> colors.txt
To find the difference between fruits.txt and Colors.txt file - diff fruits.txt colors.txt
